Class ChargingStation

java.lang.Object
ChargingStation
public class ChargingStation extends Object
Represents an EV charging station on campus. Each station includes: - an internal ID - a code (G1, L3, D2, etc.) - the lot where it is located - charger type (e.g. Level 2) - a ChargingStatus indicating real-time availability
